you just, "We will make this the focus. Speed,  

478
00:43:17,560 --> 00:43:21,840
speed, speed." I think maybe the lesson 
there is, you pick the thing that you  

479
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:27,520
think will most differentiate you, make you 
