480
00:43:27,520 --> 00:43:33,360
So just thoughts on how you decided speed 
was the thing you were going to obsess with,  

481
00:43:33,360 --> 00:43:37,800
and advice for folks that are trying to 
decide where to dial up things to 11?

482
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:43,360
Bill is right and I agree with him, you have 
to pick something. Knowing what to pick is the  

483
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:49,240
trick. In the early days of Superhuman, I read 
a book on positioning that really influenced my  

484
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:56,520
