503
00:45:44,080 --> 00:45:51,800
people pitch your product to other people. In our 
case the pitches were simple. People would say,  

504
00:45:51,800 --> 00:45:57,040
"Dude, you have to use it, it's really fucking 
fast." And that's it. That was the pitch.  

505
00:45:57,040 --> 00:46:01,240
That's how I knew that speed would be a 
really great position for us to start with.

