603
00:54:49,720 --> 00:54:55,160
to increase product market fit. 
Talk about how one would do that.

604
00:54:55,160 --> 00:55:01,880
Well, that's really the meat of the engine. 
Let's see if I can condense it here in a very  

605
00:55:01,880 --> 00:55:09,120
