631
00:57:27,120 --> 00:57:30,160
they're still pulling you in a different 
direction. And the thing that they like  

632
00:57:30,160 --> 00:57:37,160
the most from your product isn't actually what 
the people who en mass love it the most for, is. 

633
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:43,120
You have then articulated the subsegment of the 
subsegment that it makes sense to pay attention  

634
00:57:43,120 --> 00:57:48,760
to, and there's another question in the engine to 
