635
00:57:48,760 --> 00:57:52,920
Now you have a list of things people love, 
you have a list of things people don't love,  

636
00:57:52,920 --> 00:57:58,640
and you can work down that list to make 
the product market fit score go up. And  

637
00:57:58,640 --> 00:58:02,760
basically at the start of every planning cycle, 
