design. To create games, what we need to do is 
draw upon the arts and the science of psychology,  

692
01:02:48,640 --> 01:02:54,400
mathematics, storytelling, interaction design. 
And at Superhuman we've identified five key  

693
01:02:54,400 --> 01:03:01,560
areas that we really care about, goals, 
emotions, toys, controls and flow. And  

694
01:03:01,560 --> 01:03:07,800
across these we've identified many principles 
of game design. One example principle would be,  

695
01:03:07,800 --> 01:03:15,840
make fun toys and then combine those into games.
A question I like to ask is, are toys the same as  

696
01:03:15,840 --> 01:03:24,600
games? They do seem different. For example, we 
