714
01:05:08,320 --> 01:05:13,880
to do is, think about the features of their 
product. Do those features indulge, playful,  

715
01:05:13,880 --> 01:05:21,440
exploration? Are they fun even without a goal? And 
do they elicit moments of pleasant surprise? If  

716
01:05:21,440 --> 01:05:28,320
so, you have a toy and you can combine that with 
